<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes_for_Week_7:_1.1_Pricing_with_Market_Power:_An_Introduction">Notes for Week 7: 1.1 Pricing with Market Power: An Introduction</span></h2>
<p>The example of air travel industry is showcase because its innovative ways for pricing. As a case for the pricing strategies of the firms that have some market power or some degree of flexibility in pricing.</p>
<p>The main questions for this week are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Is that is this a good thing for society?</li>
<li>Are all these different pricing techniques applied by businesses because they care about their bottom line, are all these pricing techniques a good thing for, for the society?</li>
<li>Are consumers and the society in general getting better because the airline has such really interesting ways of pricing their goods?</li>
</ul>

